WEBVTT

00:00:29.738 --> 00:00:33.825
Well, you've had a busy day.

00:00:36.662 --> 00:00:38.329
So did you.

00:00:40.833 --> 00:00:43.793
Why didn't you tell me the truth
about your plan?

00:00:43.919 --> 00:00:45.962
All of it? The Moroltos.

00:00:46.588 --> 00:00:50.299
Because I knew you'd worry,
and that might make you stay.

00:00:51.635 --> 00:00:54.095
And I knew you needed to leave.

